snippet.title: Gwent Standalone Game Reveal - E3 2016 Microsoft Conference
snippet.description:
CD Projekt Red reveals the standalone version of their Witcher III card game, Gwent, with a beta coming September 2016.

Watch Microsoft’s full press conference:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2xM_NYqY71Y
